Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:03.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:04.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是推销电话就挂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:12.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是新田的妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:15.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我和新田住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:18.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:19.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,义史 刚才那个女孩子是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:26.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是听到什么幽灵在说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:27.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么… 好可怕
