Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:09.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡无奇的日常 是无可替的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:13.81,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}这份思念之情 现在终于意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:16.62,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你欢笑度过的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:19.43,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你争论泪流的曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:23.79,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们携手的每一天 令人无比怜爱的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:26.56,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:31.99,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们究竟相距多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:38.24,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回忆起你的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.05,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遥遥可见的那条街道的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:47.54,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露着笑容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:09.35,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(960,834)\pos(942,0)}第六话 新田的父亲是个花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:06.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在参拜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷子去世了 我来问候他一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷子死了吗 他不是还会动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那个老爷子 是我老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:17.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接着你要跟我家里人寒暄两句
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:18.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:21.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧 我行事很稳重的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:22.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,满心不安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:27.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我妈 和我妹妹美佳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:28.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:34.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫安达雏 我13岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸进了监狱 我无亲无故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟新田一起生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:45.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田待人很亲切 每天过得都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:51.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你是什么时候跟我哥住在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:55.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 给雏提的问题可以让我回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪来的经纪人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:58.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈那边也没有什么亲人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:06.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫安达雏 我13岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是发神经的机器人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:13.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就让我来解释 你先在外面玩会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是按着我们排练好的说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但你临场反应不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不把事情变复杂 才把你当成是借住在我这的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是暴露了惹上麻烦 我们都没什么好果子吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:25.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你就努力地呆在外边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:33.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她身上还发生过这么多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:35.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为一次打斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:38.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全家一起吃饭的时候她妈妈被枪击了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后她父亲应战后 杀掉了两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:46.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他以前经常照顾我 真是感觉坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就收留了她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏没受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她当时在吃干烧虾仁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吃干烧虾仁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:57.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:02.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是过于震惊 她就只记得当时的干烧虾仁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚收留她的时候 她几乎说不出话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:12.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但最近 她终于能慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,开始说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她刚才不是说什么每天都过得很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:23.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:28.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是她不想让我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在勉强自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 过去的事情就别再问了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干烧虾仁什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:44.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可真是不得了啊 估计有做演员的才能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:48.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,义史 差不多该吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:49.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:55.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好想吃… 义史做的饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:57.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是客人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是听说哥你要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:03.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才放心地在大白天就开始喝酒了 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这也太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我该从哪里吐槽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 我懂了 我做就是咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,烧个开水 也就三分钟的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我都用不了三分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:15.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,两分钟就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:16.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我去做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏都上初一了啊 在学校过得开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不开心 一直睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是吃午饭很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:31.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 为了让你去学校我可是花了不少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你作业应该也不做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:36.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作业…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:39.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她把作业拿过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,平时都没见她做过 在这个时候拿出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:49.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过等下 要是她开始做作业 话题也该结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好作业 非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,名字要好好写上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:58.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}新田雏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:03.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田雏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:09.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟学校那边去商量的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怕到时候因为姓不同 雏会被问东问西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:13.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到这点才让她跟我姓的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她接受了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:19.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是自然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:20.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:29.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫安达雏 我13岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥做的饭就是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:42.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但这么一看 你过得还真是挺开心的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他在一块 什么最让你开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:46.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:49.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是去夜总会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 那个… 她说她想去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:56.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 我干了蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:04.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想看到她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心就宠过头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以后要注意点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:14.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个设定还真是厉害啊 你们也太好骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:16.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也再喝点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:24.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有烟花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:29.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天有亲戚的孩子们来了 那时候剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:30.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在烧排队的蚂蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:46.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什么生物 它们都在拼命地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:54.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙 也是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:57.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:02.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个弱肉强食的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:06.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,强者会随性救人 也会随性杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真是乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:11.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟喝醉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:14.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也经常回来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:20.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你的工作说出去不太光彩 你可能也有些顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们毕竟是一家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你照顾她也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今后我们也会帮你一把的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:36.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这之前我生气把她赶了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:40.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被人骂我们不是以前分居 最近才把雏接来一起住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,坏了 坏了 醉了连个好借口都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:54.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样的话 她不就是你女儿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:58.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你没瞒着什么事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田没说谎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:08.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是… 这可是跟你的家人有关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:09.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 老妈 别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是受到很大打击 现在只记得干烧虾仁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:17.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干烧虾仁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:24.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干烧虾仁是 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,烤得吱吱响的虾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:28.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:34.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看她这样 她根本就不知道干烧虾仁是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:40.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她刚来的时候比起来 真是长大了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:46.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她虽然还是很傻 但最近也会乖乖听话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:48.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的吱吱响的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不知道干烧虾仁 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:06.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要撒这种谎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是最近才知道她是我女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:14.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心跟你们说 你们也不会相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:18.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！ 我决定不再犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:18.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:20.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,先等等 美佳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他这是认真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,详细的情况之后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:29.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 她是你的亲女儿对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 她是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,学个猥琐大叔样再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有戳 她旧是俺滴闺女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:42.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,美佳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:43.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:50.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先呢 为了新田家新添的成员干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为了咱家的新成员 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:56.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:11:00.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他爸 义史带你孙女回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:04.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 你这样的话眼神还真有点像爷爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛这是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:07.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,义史 你也来跟你爸说两句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:19.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸 虽然我没能让你见上一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:21.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但你现在有孙女了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:22.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,声太小 声太小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么小声可是传达不到天国的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今后 作为新田家一份子的雏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就有劳老爸你多多照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,义史 义史啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:37.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你会好好地爱她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:38.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:46.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今后 我也会一直好好养育她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:57.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来来 雏你也跟天国的爷爷说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:07.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其 其实没什么要说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
