Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,公园是最后的据点！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:25.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,捍卫流浪汉的生存之地！
