Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:26.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道外面的人在喊什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经瞒不住你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:41.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 你留心听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:47.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个公园 再过一阵子就不能住人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 终于也告诉杏子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然时日不长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是杏子搬过来后真的很快乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:04.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,帮她建房子的时候真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也从未觉得翻花绳是会让人那么快乐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:08.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来啊泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托诗子小姐的那件事怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:16.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已经找到愿意收养杏子的人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她今后的人生并不需要我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她能过得幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:26.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:34.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:36.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:37.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你差不多得开始收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,230)\shad0\bord0\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&H645650&\pos(1310,328)}我们就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:45.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像外面游行的人一样 我们也行动起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做这种事的话会被抓走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是板上钉钉的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要放弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:58.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔你会帮我的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来守护大家的住所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:07.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 那我自己去做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们抓不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,做那种事的话杏子你会被抓起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来会举行最后的宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把这件事忘了好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:36.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然再过不久我们的家就会没了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,致大家各自寻找到自己的新天地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:40.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:41.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我们不得不离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就一起去找别的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后大家再在那里一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他地方能像这里装得下这么多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:57.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起找的一定就能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:07.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 想和大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:09.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,开口闭口都是「大家」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了没有那种地方了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们仅仅是自己活下去就竭尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别再扯上我们了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:36.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,后藤 抱歉让你扮黑脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:40.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 才不是那么好的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:44.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是他让我觉得自己如此无能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就那她出气罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是第几次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:50.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔自己成为流浪汉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:52.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:20.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会变得难以道别的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诗子小姐 接下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:39.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:42.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:02.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你个大老爷们 别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茂叔你自己不也在哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:05.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 泰叔你也哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子就是杏子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:20.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是收留你的来来轩的林夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始就来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:26.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这装束真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:42.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么丰盛的晚餐 要花多少钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在我家吃饭不用花钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:48.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是匆匆忙忙做出来 不过听你这么说真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:17:59.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不合你口味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:06.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好吃 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:08.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:15.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一个人享用这么好吃的饭菜真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明大家都各自散去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,变成孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:29.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 别想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是先睡一觉休息一下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:36.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种要慢慢花时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能先等她熬过这阵子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:42.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:48.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要尽可能地去成为她的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:00.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:05.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经可以不用去捡易拉罐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我接下来该做些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:19.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:21.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要开店干活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:25.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:28.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要干活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用介意这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:36.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只有干活赚钱才能吃上饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事不用再做也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 孩子他妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁教你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是泰叔告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:52.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子有好好地把泰叔的教导记在心里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:59.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这不是好好活在你心里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都教会了我很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:07.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茂叔他教会我卖杂志的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:10.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳她告诉了我有易拉罐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:14.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,建房子的方法之类的 大家都教会了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其他还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其他还有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:20.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 因为人是没法只身活下去的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:24.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在杏子的心中活着很多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是孤身一人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:30.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我们会教会你各种事物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:32.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样渐渐地让你内心充盈起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:37.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 杏子一定也活在大家的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 只是单纯接受着大家的教导而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并不止是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:46.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和杏子至今为止一起生活的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有好好地存在于大家心中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:52.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 茂叔你也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:58.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很担心杏子她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:07.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然看得出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她忘记我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆地分别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:14.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们或多或少都是犯过错走到今天的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就会想这次是不是也是做错了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我认为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有愿意为我们哭泣的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:27.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再加把劲活下去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:32.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也不是孤身一人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:38.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 大家都不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:49.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:52.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 纸巾纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也给我几张
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:56.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:59.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哭成这样可没办法干活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:03.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,-ed-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:25.94,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}気がつけば　あの日のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:31.02,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出してしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:41.74,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}にぎやかな　笑顔と響く声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:48.91,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつも　今も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:54.92,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}鮮やかな色のまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:23:00.83,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}心の中に灯る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:07.97,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}この気持ちをありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:16.46,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}暖かい思い出と　共に歩くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:22.78,hinamatsuri_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何もできない　私だけと
